rg/wiki/Slack_variable" title=3D"Slack variable">slack variables</a></i> to=
 replace inequalities with equalities in the constraints. The problems can =
then be written in the following <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/B=
lock_matrix" title=3D"Block matrix">block matrix</a> form:
</p>
