<p>Khachiyan's algorithm was of landmark importance for establishing the po=
lynomial-time solvability of linear programs.  The algorithm was not a comp=
utational break-through, as the simplex method is more efficient for all bu=
t specially constructed families of linear programs.
</p><p>However, Khachiyan's algorithm inspired new lines of research in lin=
