f=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Projective_method" class=3D"mw-redirect"=
 title=3D"Projective method">projective method</a> for linear programming. =
 Karmarkar's algorithm<sup id=3D"cite_ref-karmarkar84_10-1" class=3D"refere=
nce"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Linear_programming#cite_note-=
