hiyan79_9-2" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/L=
inear_programming#cite_note-khachiyan79-9"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</=
span>9<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> worst-case polynomial=
 bound (giving <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><sp=
an class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: =
none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\disp=
laystyle O(n^{3.5}L)}">
